integrations, platforms, and delivery processes from the beginning, rather =
than
added later as a reactive control.</p>

<p style=3D'margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;line-height:15pt;font-family:"=
Segoe UI";
font-size:10.5pt'>I act as a <span style=3D'font-weight:bold'>risk-informed
design authority</span> who translates business needs, technical realities,
regulatory obligations, and threat exposure into practical security
requirements, architecture decisions, and assurance expectations.</p>

<p style=3D'margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;line-height:15pt;font-family:"=
Segoe UI";
font-size:10.5pt'>My role is not only to identify security gaps, but also to
